column2: Enable 'Return Cores' decisions

The Return Cores decisions allow you to return cores of vassals and spherelings, as long as you don't have a core in the province, and are otherwise kept hidden from view to avoid having them clutter up your decision list.
Disable 'Return Cores' decisions
Your decision list will now be uncluttered.
Deactivate 'Return Cores' decisions
The 'Return Cores' decisions will disappear from this game session and won't reappear again. You won't be able to use these decisions again for this game.
Return cores to Manipur
We hold provinces that Manipur has claims on. Returning these provinces, as an act of good faith, would surely bolster our relations.
